Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分班结果会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定又是澪一个人被分到别的班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我才不要那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  冲击性的结果！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:49.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…完全看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微失礼一下  我钻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔倒了～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  结果怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我们大家都在同一个班级哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心  鼻涕流下来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样去上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢  澪 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年级是和大家同一个班…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能多坚持一会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把布和剪子组合到一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和也和我们一个班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像会变成很热闹的班级啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个班级真好～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有谁刻意安排大家聚在一起似的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊  太巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使用了学生会长的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没有  怎么可能会有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同学  回到各自的座位去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从我成为老师以来第一次做班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会有很多不足之处  但请大家多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很幸运啊  山中老师做班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人又漂亮又温和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能只被外表所蒙蔽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和实际上是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田井中同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要窃窃私语哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有些事情想问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次分班  难道小佐和做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我把大家分到一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗  不算滥用职权吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  你们不高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴是高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能少记几个人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原来是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常高兴  谢谢你  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  你稍微平静一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  因为这样一来高中最后一年能和大家在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在一个班是很高兴的事 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也得考虑一下将来的出路什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  修学旅行也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭的班级发表也是一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让大家帮我在考试前复习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业也能让我抄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人兴奋不已啊  三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  开学典礼马上就要开始了 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去大礼堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就待会儿见了  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳不已啊  三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴高采烈啊  三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐唱校歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:10:04.11,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澄みし碧空　仰ぎ見て
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:13.78,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥けき理想を　結ばんと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:23.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香れる桜花の　咲く丘に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:34.05,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　励みし友垣が集う校庭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:54.19,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連なる美峯の懐に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:11:03.72,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慈愛の精神を育みて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:13.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開けゆく未来を担わんと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:24.17,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ああ　勉めし友垣が集う校庭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:10:04.11,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬头仰望这片清澈的青空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:13.78,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接着遥远的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:23.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在芬芳的樱花盛开的山丘上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:34.05,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  互相激励的朋友们聚集着的校园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:54.19,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在连绵不断的美丽山峰的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:11:03.72,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育了慈爱的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:13.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担负着敞开的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:24.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  互相学习的朋友们聚集着的校园
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在为什么而鼓劲呢  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要招揽到新部员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  和和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还差一个就是一打了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那我先去学生会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  新生欢迎演出的练习完后我就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新部员加入就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就现在这样也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们毕业后就只剩下小梓一个人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  振作一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了梓喵  轻音部也得加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是活动室里舒服啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在春假的时候也有好多次想跑到这里来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！  新学期我们该干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉新部员入伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃的蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逗你玩的啦  真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！请认真一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊  小律！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有新部员的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年可就只剩梓喵一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:12:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嘴上这么说着却一副悠闲到家的姿势啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话明年你可就当定部长了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:07.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当…当不当部长都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑补了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑补了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这个了  我们还是快点去找新部员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敷衍过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急忙敷衍过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有做传单哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我家小忧的主意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.79,0:13:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我是猪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是轻音猪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（轻音部嘛（けいおんぶだ）与轻音猪（けいおんぶた）发音相近）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说是「轻音部」和「猪」的发音重叠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  多发点传单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要参加轻音部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去明年又要被废部啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下梓喵一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐…我好寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能被废部！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  部员增加的话部费也会随之上涨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼唧哼唧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:17.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（ブヒブヒ（猪叫声）和部費（ぶひ）发音相同）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞！  部员捕获大作战现在正式开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼唧～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  请问你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  音乐室…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能扶我去那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧  已经到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…欢迎来到轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在这里签名！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们还有急事！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有饼干！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路边晕倒作战失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  现在放弃还太早了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问音乐室在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变方言了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被告知怎么去音乐室的路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  一般确实会那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是间谍大作战！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过入部体验
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习其他社团是如何拉拢新人的对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以柔克刚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓柔道就是锻炼技力  磨练心智的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬出精神论啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想加入柔道部看看啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适得其反啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天地万物自在棋盘之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苦  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些社团都好有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要看看这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（超自然研究会）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春的汗水…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还有入部特典
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…怎么是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传单都发完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们那边怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥成果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  你们就这身打扮去的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有原则啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…怎么是小佐和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的新生欢迎演出  你们准备穿什么上台？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花边迷你裙女仆装！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服就好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很合身的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…和和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？在试衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于明天的新生欢迎演出…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  曲目顺序这样就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#（吐槽：第三首是啥-  -  新歌？  いちごパフェが止まらない  草莓冷糕停不下来）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:02.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}1.我的爱是订书机\N2.毛笔与圆珠笔\N3.草莓冷糕停不下来（新曲？）\N4.软软呼呼Time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  出这首曲子的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵是听了那时候的演出才决定参加轻音部的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年一定也有和梓喵有同样想法的人！  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得…应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…会有…的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么呢？唯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经到演出的时间了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！就看这场演出啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  测试测试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位新生  欢迎大家入学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对很合身的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们组建了一支叫作「放学后茶会」的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然每天都在喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家一起玩音乐是一件很快乐的事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果感兴趣的话  请一定加入轻音部！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还赶得上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:15.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的演出真赞！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓和唯的吉他也配得相当不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然唯好像把全部力气都用光爬不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼唧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要这样  学姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来还要发传单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:18:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去发传单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  去一下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再出去发一次传单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊  为什么没人来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了方便来这社团教室我还特意设了标记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐！把这个收起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:17.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（欢迎来到轻音部）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个多好啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小气  小气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有新部员加入吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是轻音部没什么人气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生欢迎演出很帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多新生都这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因为轻音部五个人看上去非常团结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人很难插进去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是…那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家那么融洽  很愉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:19:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说因为那个？  嗅到了轻音部可疑的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忧的炒蛋看上去很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尝尝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也没有新部员来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是做了什么坏事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有办法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那考虑下一个作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕虫网大作战之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用捕虫网  然后这样  这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样怎么可能抓到人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得暂时这样也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就这样挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  大家都聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…虽然现在梓喵不在啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶  练习  演奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:53.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五个人一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩一年呢  总有办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你们讲  一年很快的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  有365天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.48,0:21:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经过了几天了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  今天的点心是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都要什么味道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好选啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看梓喵一定会选香蕉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把香蕉的留给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要橘子味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜瓜蜜瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香草是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要草莓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这个很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉  马上就去发传单
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐  我要奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有香蕉蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我决定还是5个人一起走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后要严加努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:22:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  拿出吉他来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新部员还是快降临吧～！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.26,0:23:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我们来大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.34,0:23:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈  好像很贵重的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.13,0:23:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有装什么值钱的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是能轻松整理旧杂志的纸胶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.68,0:23:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这样好吗  大家分？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.13,0:24:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法吧  小佐和都说用作部费了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼唧哼唧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.45,0:24:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪个社团都有新部员加入并正式开始活动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.88,0:24:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.70,0:24:09.71,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}#2　　整顿 !


